{"id":232943801,"title":"富士新鏡-低配版35mm F2","content":"富士在今天發表了一機兩鏡\n分別是X-T100的後繼機種X-T200\nGFX系統的恆定光圈變焦鏡GF 45-100 F4\n還有應該比較多人會在意的XC 35 F2\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5412abbd-f182-4ab8-bd3c-90bf93604dc0/1280.jpeg\n從規格來看基本上可以看作是XF35 F2的低配版本\n有著一樣的鏡組配置（六群九片含兩非球面鏡片）與對焦馬達，濾鏡口徑一樣是43mm\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6bb34eaa-c0eb-49aa-b7de-137a76f02bb1/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9109a395-e34e-4ad3-8d90-629f82bb6f48/full.jpeg\n差別在於XC35用上了塑膠卡口（鏡身似乎也是）、沒有了防滴塵以及光圈環，也因此重量比XF35輕了40公克（170克vs130克），價格據傳也便宜近一半\n如果能用一半的價格買到相同的光學素質相比也是相當有競爭力\n\n不過我更希望富士能出35/23 1.4的二代或類似XC這種低配版本😂","excerpt":"富士在今天發表了一機兩鏡，分別是X-T100的後繼機種X-T200，GFX系統的恆定光圈變焦鏡GF 45-100 F4，還有應該比較多人會在意的XC 35 F2，從規格來看基本上可以看作是XF35 F","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d0cd5819-4627-4b5f-8a8e-050976e0fba1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-23T09:13:33.430Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-23T09:13:33.430Z","commentCount":3,"likeCount":7,"tags":[],"topics":["富士","相機","攝影器材","鏡頭"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"攝影","forumAlias":"photography","school":"國立高雄大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":7}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5412abbd-f182-4ab8-bd3c-90bf93604dc0/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/6bb34eaa-c0eb-49aa-b7de-137a76f02bb1/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9109a395-e34e-4ad3-8d90-629f82bb6f48/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"fab3652e-c245-45ca-9120-ddd285540337","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5412abbd-f182-4ab8-bd3c-90bf93604dc0/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/5412abbd-f182-4ab8-bd3c-90bf93604dc0/640.jpeg","t